# homework 1
## Calculate the distance from one page to another page. Write your code in find_shortest_path().
### Example
* Input: "池袋", "渋谷"
```
Path found: ["池袋", "渋谷"]
```
* Input: "コロラドハイツ大学", "魚沼田中駅"
```
Path found: ["コロラドハイツ大学", "1988年", "10月1日", "只見線", "魚沼田中駅"]
```
